				</div>
				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div role="note" class="hatnote">For other persons named Thomas Day, see <a href="/wiki/Thomas_Day_(disambiguation)" class="mw-disambig" title="Thomas Day (disambiguation)">Thomas Day (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
