<dd>*Jefferson, Cord, <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.npr.org/2013/04/30/177764747/a-british-intellectuals-mission-to-create-the-perfect-wife">"A British Intellectual's Mission 'To Create The Perfect Wife'" (review)</a>, <a href="/wiki/NPR" title="NPR">NPR</a>, 30 April 2013.</dd>
